title: Public Sale Option A for members participating in testnet - [No Vesting, Fully Unlocked]
body:
Public Sale Option A for members participating in testnet - [No Vesting, Fully Unlocked]. This option allows participants to purchase tokens at $0.15/token, with no lockups. In order to prevent concentration, incentivize distribution, and incentivize tokens for staking, this allocation will enforce a maximum check size of $5K USD.
Public Sale Option B - [1 Year Vesting]. This option allows participants to purchase tokens at $0.10/token, using a 1 year vesting schedule, with quarterly unlocking. There is a maximum check size of $10K USD for this allocation.
